{"tid":1879270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵御用保安公司國際永勝Q3 業績，臨時保安護衛服務，收入金額是1.46億元！","createTime":"2020-02-14T05:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T04:59:02.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ce960cba1975d6fa1b835dc2313d975a46f3791f","tid":1879270,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"「黨鐵寄生族」、御用保安公司國際永勝（8441）出咗Q3 業績，來自港鐵（66）臨時專責保安護衛服務，收入金額是驚人的1.46億元！<br />\n<br />\n翻查新聞，港鐵9月底聲稱只增加500個保安應對，但國際永勝竟可以從港鐵身上取得1.46億元，難道保安個個天價？時薪高過李小龍？<br />\n<br />\n想多了，翻查報導，國際永勝2018年的招聘廣告，西九龍高鐵站外圍保安只是每月17,000元，而2019年3月西九站巡邏保安員每月11,056元。<br />\n<br />\n可想而知，這份黨鐵天價合同，絕大部分利潤，也是被這間公司由「小巴大王」馬亞木所蠶食，保安也是被他所剝削！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ti7mYuu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTi7mYuu.png&h=7f9698ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/&hellip;/gem/2020/0211/2020021100673_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fgem%2F2020%2F0211%2F2020021100673_c.pdf&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=ce34bffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/&hellip;/gem/2020/0211/2020021100673_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/11mister/photos/a.600943543346928/2681574778617117/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F11mister%2Fphotos%2Fa.600943543346928%2F2681574778617117%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=4a511863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/11mister/photos/a.600943543346928/2681574778617117/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e0e740a04da61a9c8abd71b5bde9b602087ae8d8","tid":1879270,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"小巴都盡量唔好坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef246ed6ffb6